	 experts and newbies of startups in Greater Houston! Past topics include: 
	\nTraction + Funding Stage Identification – What stage are you really at?\
	nICP – Seeking your beachhead market\nProblem Identification – Love the pr
	oblem\, not the solution\nBootstrapping – Knowing your runway and not putt
	ing money on fire. 🔥\nFounder capacity\, 10xing and recruiting for your we
	aknesses. 🚀\n\nLinkedIn Group: https://www.linkedin.com/groups/16537030/\n
